    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/part-i/article-v/section-507"
             temporalId="sSection 507">
      <num>Section 507</num>
      <heading>Meetings of the council</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The council shall, by ordinance, provide for the time and place of holding its meetings
               and the manner in which its special meetings may be called.</p>
      </content>
    </section>
